## How to run: 
# on macOS in terminal type follow the steps:
  - cd choose folder
  - npm i
  - nodemon  

## About database
  - use Compass
  - Database name is newage 
  - Collection name: newages

# About app
  - App writen in Nodejs;
  - Framework is ejs;
  - Databese - Mongodb;
  - Full ORM;
  - Full API and crud opps;
  - Error handling by try catch

# Third party packages
  - Mongoose, email-validator, dotenv, cookie-session  

